{
  "texts": [
    "The output logits, when transformed via a softmax, provide an uncalibrated probability distribution over codons.",
    "The language model is trained using a masked language modelling (MLM) objective 57:",
    "For each sequence x, we sample a percentage of the set of positions ℳ where the true token at index i is replaced with another token and we independently minimize the negative log likelihood of the true codon given the masked sequence.",
    "Model training.",
    "We trained the model using dynamic masking 59."
  ]
}